            <title><![CDATA[【感染新冠病毒后会留下后遗症吗？专家解答来[话筒]】近段时间以来，新冠病毒二次感染的话题引起大家的关注。一些人感染新冠病毒康复后，可能会在短期内存在乏力...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【感染新冠病毒后会留下后遗症吗？专家解答来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】近段时间以来，新冠病毒二次感染的话题引起大家的关注。一些人感染新冠病毒康复后，可能会在短期内存在乏力、心跳加速、肺功能下降等症状，有人因此担心，感染新冠病毒后会留下后遗症。对此，国务院联防联控机制组织专家进行了解答👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫疫点通#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4907035293319203" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">健康中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0035PbOdly1heg6byjuakj60zk0k0tcc02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6dTG8XYHlx085Q01pJA401041200EEW40E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685453598&amp;ssig=FHsuXSyjbT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/phcZ0HzLlx085Q00LOvu01041200kHg40E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685453598&amp;ssig=nsI8hxCYdZ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/spe4gncJlx085Q00EHMs01041200dHHx0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685453598&amp;ssig=Drt%2BeQKr%2B%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4907035293319203&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
